{
  "stem": "15115.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You see, they'd done it in Poland, and they'd done it in Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They did all these countries that went ahead of time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when they came to-- it was a special commando, they came to Salonika, because in Salonika 87% or 88% of the Jews of Greece.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was the main object there was to take the Jews from Greece.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as I would say, that's about the size of it that I remember in Greece that the time that we suffered.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a lot of people died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of people-- hunger, people dying in the streets, swollen legs from having no food, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like a lot dead people, Jewish people died daily.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A lot of people, as I was telling you before, they were coming from-- they were working, like where my brother was, inside Greece.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were coming in dead, they would bring them into the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Throw their bodies in the synagogue, on the four steps of the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were people who'd come and pick up the bodies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was the beginning of the end, was that, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When they-- when the Greeks started coming back from the labor in Greece, I could see that was the beginning of the end.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they started gathering us into ghettos, as I said.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They started taking the-- we used to have about six or seven sections of Jews, different groups-- different ghettos.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Not like ghettos, I mean, they used to live together, like poor Jews, rich Jews, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "First they started taking all the poor Jews, which is they started number 109.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Those Jews were original in Baron Hirsch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was-- Baron Hirsch was a Jewish poor section.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
